## 📌 Milestone 2: Data Cleaning & Preprocessing

### 🎯 Objective
Prepare raw data for analysis by handling inconsistencies and missing values.

### 🛠️ Tasks Performed
- Removed duplicate records
- Handled missing/null values
- Converted date columns into proper datetime format
- Standardized categorical values (Priority, Status, Issue Type)
- Removed irrelevant columns:
  - First Response Time
  - Time to Resolution (if inconsistent)

### 🔍 Data Transformation
- Created new features:
  - Resolution Time (calculated)
  - Ticket Age
- Ensured consistent formatting across dataset

### ⚠️ Challenges Faced
- Inconsistent status labels
- Missing resolution timestamps
- Data type mismatches

### ✅ Outcome
Clean and structured dataset ready for exploratory data analysis (EDA).
